    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a fantastic project! This vehicle is the perfect choice for a mechanic or a DIY enthusiast looking for a budget-friendly entry into car ownership. While it definitely needs some significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back to its best, it offers a great foundation for someone ready to put in the work and bring it back to life!",
