    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with this absolute gem, and honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape. It has been pampered since day one\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure driving bliss. It basically looks and feels brand new! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and kept in pristine condition, you\u2019ve gotta see this one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
