    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional 997.2 Carrera S, a pinnacle of the naturally aspirated, hydraulic-steering era. This specimen is powered by the 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six, paired with a sought-after 6-speed manual transaxle and a factory mechanical limited-slip differential. The vehicle features Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) with a lowered ride height for superior damping and roll stiffness. A comprehensive DME report shows zero ignitions in ranges 4-6, confirming sympathetic ownership. The exterior boasts original paint with uniform micrometer readings, while the interior remains factory-fresh. All maintenance is current, including recent fluid analysis and spark plug interval service. This is a collector-grade example with zero mechanical compromises.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
