    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2015 Porsche Cayman S is a true museum-quality specimen, preserved in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The Agate Grey Metallic paint retains its deep, factory luster with zero swirls or stone chips, protected by a full-front clear bra. Inside, the black leather interior remains taut and fragrant, showing no bolster wear or sun fading. Every service has been performed exclusively at authorized Porsche centers, documented in a comprehensive binder included with the sale. Mechanically, it is flawless\u2014the PDK shifts are lightning-fast, and the flat-six engine sings without a hint of hesitation. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a showroom-new driving machine.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
